He's got missile lock on us!

84
00:07:43,912 --> 00:07:45,174
Get away from this guy!

85
00:07:45,213 --> 00:07:47,340
What is this shit?
He's engaging me.

86
00:07:49,518 --> 00:07:51,418
Damn it, Mustang,
this is Ghost Rider.

87
00:07:51,453 --> 00:07:54,422
This bogey's all over me.
He's got missile lock on me.

88
00:07:54,456 --> 00:07:55,821
Permission to fire?

89
