Don't fire until fired upon.

90
00:08:00,295 --> 00:08:01,785
Goose, there they are below us.

91
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,889
The MIG's in perfect
firing position.

92
00:08:03,932 --> 00:08:05,399
He's right on Cougar's tail.

93
00:08:05,434 --> 00:08:07,265
No way, Goose.
He'd have fired already.

94
00:08:07,302 --> 00:08:08,826
He's trying to piss us off.

95
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:11,566
Maverick, get down here
and get this asshole off me.

96
00:08:14,142 --> 00:08:15,837
Easy, Cougar.

97
00:08:15,877 --> 00:08:17,868
Bring him back. Hard right.

98
00:08:17,913 --> 00:08:19,403
Help me engage.

99
00:08:20,616 --> 00:08:21,947
