MIG-1 has bugged out.

109
00:09:17,596 --> 00:09:18,028
MIG-1 has bugged out.

110
00:09:20,132 --> 00:09:22,123
[Breathing erratically]

111
00:09:27,572 --> 00:09:29,631
Cougar, this is Maverick.

112
00:09:29,674 --> 00:09:32,507
We've had enough fun
for one day, don't you think?

113
00:09:32,544 --> 00:09:35,707
I'm getting a little low
on fuel, so we're heading home.

114
00:09:38,984 --> 00:09:40,542
We'll see you on deck.

115
00:09:49,828 --> 00:09:52,228
We're running Low on gas.
We've gotta get out of here.

116
00:09:52,964 --> 00:09:54,659
[Beeping]

117
00:09:54,699 --> 00:09:56,064
Cougar.

118
00:09:58,403 --> 00:10:00,371
We're on vapor, Cougar.

119
00:10:00,405 --> 00:10:02,066
Let's do it.

120
00:10:04,409 --> 00:10:05,899
Cougar! Come on, Cougar!

121
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,885
MERLIN: Take it back
to the ship, man.

122
00:10:16,922 --> 00:10:18,048
Come on, Cougar.

123
00:10:18,089 --> 00:10:20,216
Get him on deck
as soon as possible.

124
00:10:20,258 --> 00:10:21,953
He's gotta be Low on fuel.

125
00:10:24,062 --> 00:10:26,053
Cougar, we've got to land
this thing.

126
00:10:26,097 --> 00:10:29,533
We are way Low on gas,
you understand me?

127
00:10:29,568 --> 00:10:31,433
You all right, man?

128
